Each project README should include:

* project overview;
* objective;
* architecture;
* class and module descriptions;
* algorithm description;
* interface description;
* build instructions;
* execution instructions;
* test procedure;
* example output;
* performance results;
* limitations;
* planned improvements.

Larger projects should also contain:

* architecture diagrams;
* class diagrams;
* sequence diagrams;
* data-flow diagrams;
* state diagrams;
* API documentation;
* verification results;
* benchmark results.

